{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Place Varoma dish into position and weigh in shrimp, secure Varoma lid and set aside.","Place garlic, shallots and parsley into mixing bowl and chop <b>5 sec\/speed 7<b>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula.","Add butter, seafood stock, lemon juice, salt and pepper. Place Varoma into position and steam <b>10 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<b>. Remove lid and stir seafood with spatula to ensure even cooking. Secure Varoma lid and steam a further <b>5-7 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<b> until shrimp is cooked through. Remove Varoma and set aside.","Insert measuring cup and mix <b>5 sec\/speed 3<b>. Transfer garlic sauce and steamed shrimp to serving dish and serve immediately."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["32 oz shrimp, raw, peeled and deveined (thawed if frozen)","½ - 1 oz garlic cloves (approx.  5-8 cloves)","2 oz shallots, cut into pieces","½ oz parsley, leaves only","8 oz unsalted butter","2 oz seafood stock","2 oz lemon juice","½ tsp fine sea salt","½ tsp ground black pepper"]}],"id":"r157493","imageLink":"https:\/\/4.bp.blogspot.com\/-D3EWBOhYino\/XZVPZvvXrrI\/AAAAAAAAc4Q\/LNyV-fW-ezkTrj5y4Ki95yCGr-FBgfmkwCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_5ztWW_ysY8wkWXb9.png","title":"Garlic Shrimp","publishedAt":"2017-03-24T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"32 g","fat":"48 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"6 g","calories":"2452 kJ \/ 586 kcal"},"usefulItems":"serving dish","hintsAndTricks":["Serve with steamed rice, linguine or simply with buttered crusty bread."],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","35m","4 portions"]}